original: Lindeström, Karl-Erik Edmund, tandläkare. Mariestad, f. 22/10/12 i Linköp. av Knut L. o. Sara Andersson. G. m. tandl. Stina Frykholm. Barn: Maj-Britt f. 33, Lars-Erik 44, Ulla 45. — Stud:ex. i Linköp. 31, tandl :ex. 43. Distr:tandl. i Värml. län 44, praktik i Mariestad sed. 47.
translated: Lindeström, Karl-Erik Edmund, dentist. Born in Mariestad on October 22, 1912 in Linköping, son of Knut L. and Sara Andersson. Married to dentist Stina Frykholm. Children: Maj-Britt born in 1933, Lars-Erik in 1944, Ulla in 1945. Completed high school in Linköping in 1931, obtained dental degree in 1943. Worked as a district dentist in Värmland County in 1944 and has been practicing in Mariestad since 1947.
